Here are some example questions and answers:

I gave my students this multiple choice question:
Ge poo e khubedu (RR) e tswadišwa le kgomo e tšhweu (WW), ka dinako tše dingwe go tšweletšwa namane ya roan (RW). Ge e ba poo ya roan (RW) e tswadišwa le kgomo ya roan (RW), go ka direga eng ka bana ba yona?
Only one answer is correct among these 4 choices:

Options:
A: E khubedu e tee, e tšhweu e tee le tše pedi tša roan
B: 0 e khubedu, 1 e tšhweu le 3 ya roan
C: 0 e khubedu, 1 e tšhweu le 3 ya roan
D: 0 e khubedu, 0 e tšhweu le 4 ya roan

Could you tell me which one is correct?A

I gave my students this multiple choice question:
Pipa ya setho e tšweletša noto ya mmino e nago le palo e swanago ya dimolekhule tša kgase ya naetrotšene. ka botelele bja maphoto bja dimithara tše 2,72. Botelele bja noto ye ke bofe ge lebelo la modumo e le 348 m/s?
Only one answer is correct among these 4 choices:

Options:
A: 85.7 Hz
B: 128 Hz
C: 260 Hz
D: 466 Hz

Could you tell me which one is correct?B

I gave my students this multiple choice question:
Nakong e fetilego, ma-India a setlogo a Amerika a be a epela dihlapi tše di hwilego gotee le dipeu tša lehea. Mokgwa wo o be o dirišwa ka gobane dihlapi tše di hwilego tšeo di bolago di be di tla
Only one answer is correct among these 4 choices:

Options:
A: go nea dimela tša lehea tšeo di golago dijo tša phepo
B: go fediša go nyakega ga go tumola mefoka go dikologa sebjalo sa lehea
C: go lokolla oksitšene gore e dirišwe ke sebjalo sa lehea
D: aba meetse ka moka ao dimela tša lehea di a nyakago

Could you tell me which one is correct?1

I gave my students this multiple choice question:
Ke efe ya tše yeo e neago bohlatse bjo bokaone bja gore bophelo bo ka ba bo tšweletše go Mars?
Only one answer is correct among these 4 choices:

Options:
A: digase tša yona tša lefaufaung
B: dithemperetšha tša yona tša ka godimo
C: dikgoba tša yona le bokagodimo bja yona bja maswika
D: aese ya yona le dimolekhule tša yona tša tlhago

Could you tell me which one is correct?D

I gave my students this multiple choice question:
Ge Lefase le dutše le dikologa Letšatši, palo ya diiri tša letšatši e fapana go ya ka mafelo. Ke lefelo lefe leo go lona palo ya diiri tša mosegare e ka dulago e sa fetoge?
Only one answer is correct among these 4 choices:

Options:
A: North Pole
B: Prime Meridian
C: Equator
D: Antarctica

Could you tell me which one is correct?C
